desc: We are a Sydney Northern Beaches movement studio, offering a variety of Yoga classes including vinyasa and yin yoga. We also offer Barre Attack classes, Mat pilates and designated room for reformer pilates. Our beautiful facility also offers free child minding during certain hours.

layout.text: Our larger community at Chocolate Box Training have created an Online program that includes our classes so you can stay active and stretchy during your Covid-19 Isolation period.
